description:
My HoneyDew this week is Matt Fulchiron - host of The Full Charge Power Hour, AKA The Full Charge AKA The Concierge AKA Your Baby’s Daddy! Matt shares stories about growing up in Southern Maryland, taking sex ed in Catholic school, and what it was like moving from Los Angeles to a crummy New York apartment where he lived in a hallway and took a less than ideal job as a receptionist at a hair salon!
